    <Folder id="237">
      <name>Tiber Upstream - Head of the Lake</name>
      <open>1</open>
      <description>rownative.icu
11 km practice course above the dam on the River Tiber

Largest head race in the west. Held in early November. Starts in Lake Union, near the I-5 bridge and finishes near the UW boathouse.</description>
